OL,3,CXL Bully shot dead by police in
OL,4,CScotland after three people injured
OL,6,FThe elderly dog had a lucky escape
OL,7,Fthanks to a teenage boy, who prised
OL,8,Fopen the XL Bully's jaws and rescued
OL,9,Fthe Collie.
OL,11,FPolice Scotland attempted to restrain
OL,12,Fthe "dangerously out of control" dog.
OL,13,FOfficers fired multiple shots and the
OL,14,Fdog was killed.
OL,16,FThree people were injured during the
OL,17,Fincident.
