OL,3,CXL Bully shot dead by police in
OL,4,CScotland after three people injured
OL,6,FWhile Police Scotland is yet to
OL,7,Fofficially establish the breed of the
OL,8,Fdog, ITV News can confirm it was an XL
OL,9,FBully named Kilo.
OL,11,FThe dog had recently been brought to
OL,12,FScotland from England to evade the ban
OL,13,Fon XL Bullies there, ITV News
OL,14,Funderstands.
OL,16,FIn a statement Police Scotland said:
OL,17,F"Enquiries are ongoing to establish
OL,18,Fthe breed of dog and there will be a
OL,19,Fcontinued police presence in the area
OL,20,Fwhile enquiries continue.
