OL,11,FXL - Bully ban is England versus
OL,12,FScotland
OL,14,FIn England it is illegal for XL Bully
OL,15,Fdogs to be without a muzzle in public.
OL,17,FThis is not the case in Scotland yet
OL,18,Fbecause the Scottish government chose
OL,19,Fnot to immediately follow the ban on
OL,20,Fthe breed.
