OL,6,FOwners of XL-Bully's then moved their
OL,7,Fdogs to Scotland en masse from England
OL,8,Fto escape the ban.
OL,10,FBut this has now forced the Scottish
OL,11,Fgovernment to u-turn on their policy
OL,12,Fand ban bullies.
OL,14,FThe new rules will start coming into
OL,15,Fforce until this Friday.
